{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, all our conclusions §6 are based on empirical analysis.",
    "While this provides robust evidence, it may not capture all aspects of the problem.",
    "Lastly, as with any survey, our interpretations and conclusions §5 are influenced by our own perspectives and understanding of the field.",
    "Other researchers might interpret the same studies differently.",
    "Despite these limitations, we believe this study provides a valuable overview of the current state of puzzle-solving using reasoning of Large Language Models."
  ]
